title: Milos Calic
text:
Milos Calic (born 31 August 1992) is a <a href="Serbian%20people">Serbian</a> <a href="rugby%20league">rugby league</a> player who plays for <a href="Villefranche%20XIII%20Aveyron">Villefranche XIII Aveyron</a> in the <a href="Elite%20Two%20Championship">Elite Two Championship</a> He plays as a .
Career.
Red Star.
He started his career at <a href="Red%20Star%20Rugby%20League%20Club">Red Star</a>
Villeneuve.
Calic and Villeneuve teammate <a href="Vladica%20Nikolic">Vladica Nikolic</a> were both signed from Serbian rugby league club <a href="Red%20Star%20Rugby%20League%20Club">Red Star</a>.
Villefranche XIII Aveyron.
On 22 Oct 2019 it was reported that he had signed for <a href="Villefranche%20XIII%20Aveyron">Villefranche XIII Aveyron</a> in the <a href="Elite%20Two%20Championship">Elite Two Championship</a>
International.
He made his international début on 3 Jul 2010 v <a href="Germany%20national%20rugby%20league%20team">Germany</a> in a 40-14 victory
